<div class="contyishang">
<div style="height:30px; font-weight:bold; font-size:16px; margin-bottom:10px; clear:both;">
<h2><span style="float:left;">创作背景</span></h2>
<a style="float:left; margin-top:7px; margin-left:5px;" href="javascript:PlayShangxi(36218)"><img id="speakerimgShangxi36218" src="/img/speaker.png" / alt="" width="16" height="16"/></a>
<span id="shangxiPlay36218" style=" display:none;width:1px; height:1px; float:left;"></span>
</div>
　　关于此<a href="https://so.gushiwen.org/shiwenv_921d278e4ef5.aspx">诗</a>，《毛诗序》、方玉润《诗经原始》、范家相《诗渖》等以为是卫女思归之作，而何楷《诗经世本古义》、龚橙《诗本谊》、<a href="https://so.gushiwen.org/authorv_bca3720a3f41.aspx" target="_blank">魏源</a>《诗古微》、高亨《诗经今注》等以为是许穆公夫人所作，<a href="https://so.gushiwen.org/authorv_fe616ed2242d.aspx" target="_blank">黄中</a>松《诗疑辨证》则怀疑是宋桓夫人或邢侯夫人所作。
</div>
<div class="dingpai">
<a id="dingsx36218" href="javascript:dingsx('36218','http://so.gushiwen.org/shiwenv.aspx?id=921d278e4ef5')">有用(3)</a><a id="paisx36218" style=" margin-left:10px;" href="javascript:paisx('36218','http://so.gushiwen.org/shiwenv.aspx?id=921d278e4ef5')">没用(0)</a>
